anded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-nav\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg><span class=\"sr-only\">Toggle menu</span></button></div></header><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-glacier\"><div class=\"relative h-[40vh] min-h-[40vh] w-full overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2400%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/40\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center px-6\"><h1 class=\"max-w-4xl text-center font-heading text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-glacier\">Sustainability &amp; local impact</h1></div></div><main class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-[1440px] flex-1 px-8 pb-24 pt-12 md:px-20 md:pt-14\"><div class=\"mb-12 rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8\"><p class=\"max-w-4xl text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-lg\">How Unitech Hydropower frames its mandate — from company-context.md, without inventing metrics.</p></div><div class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/90 md:text-[17px] md:leading-8 [&amp;_strong]:font-semibold [&amp;_strong]:text-brand-blue\"><section class=\"space-y-20 py-20 first:pt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-10\"><p>Unitech Hydropower Company Limited describes its mission as producing<!-- --> <strong>clean, renewable hydroelectricity</strong>by using Nepal&#x27;s water resources efficiently, with<!-- --> <strong>modern technology</strong> and<!-- --> <strong>environmental responsibility</strong> aligned to sustainable infrastructure practice.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-10\"><p>Beyond electrons, the company&#x27;s stated approach includes<!-- --> <strong>socio-economic development</strong>: creating employment, supporting <strong>local communities</strong> in project-affected areas, and contributing to regional development and livelihoods.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-10\"><p>Operationally, the <strong>Upper Phawa Khola</strong> asset is a run-of-river configuration with documented civil and hydraulic design elements (weir, desanding, headrace, surge, penstock, tailrace) intended to manage sediment and hydraulic transients responsibly — expand technical copy only with engineer-reviewed material.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-10\"><p>The <strong>Middle Iwa / Iwa Khola</strong> project remains in feasibility and licensing stages; avoid implying delivered community outcomes until backed by published ESIA or community development agreements.</p></div></section></div></main></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"border-t border-white/20 bg-brand-blue-deep text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-[1440px] flex-col gap-10 px-8 py-14 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between md:px-20\"><div class=\"max-w-md space-y-3\"><p class=\"font-heading text-lg font-bold tracking-tight\">Unitech Hydropower Company Limited</p><p class=\"font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/80\">Nepal-based energy development focused on clean, renewable hydroelectricity and responsible hydropower delivery.</p><p class=\"font-sans text-xs text-white/55\">Public figures on this site are aligned with internal company disclosures and regulatory filings.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12\"><div><h2 class=\"font-heading text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-cyan\">Capacity</h2><p class=\"mt-3 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85\"><span class=\"font-semibold tabular-nums text-white\">5.8 MW</span> <!-- -->Operational<span class=\"text-white/55\"> · </span><span class=\"font-semibold tabular-nums text-white\">15 MW</span> <!-- -->Pipeline</p></div><div><h2 class=\"font-heading text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-cyan\">Project sites</h2><p class=\"mt-3 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85\">Taplejung &amp; Panchthar, Nepal</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-white/10 py-4 text-center text-xs text-white/50\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Unitech Hydropower Company Limited. All rights reserved.</div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14_of.tohpz1y.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[3020,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.knbrh_.9x37.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0r_kwm7y4lawv.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"SiteHeader\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.knbrh_.9x37.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0r_kwm7y4lawv.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.knbrh_.9x37.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0r_kwm7y4lawv.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n9:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.knbrh_.9x37.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0r_kwm7y4lawv.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0kbit~ah5.901.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/0c795a286deabae8-s.p.14tvuu96~wkr0.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/83afe278b6a6bb3c-s.p.0q-301v4kxxnr.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"impact\\\"],\\\"q\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"impact\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",16],[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0kbit~ah5.901.css\\\",\\\"precedence\\\":\\\"n